title: Fire & Blood: The Shivers & The Winter Fever (2019)
description:
Edited audio from the livestream on Jan 22nd 2019. With guests JoeMagician and InDeepGeek, we discuss the many possibilities for disease and winter in ASOIAF. A chilling chat, to be sure.
